link.description: The Elocity HIEV Canada mobile app provides a user-friendly interface for managing electric vehicle (EV) charging. The app enables you to locate charging stations, monitor charging sessions in real time, and manage payments securely. Additional features include session history, energy consumption insights, and notifications for charging status updates. Designed for reliability and ease of use, the app enhances the EV charging experience by offering essential tools for efficient and seamless operations.
